{"tid":1541900,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位手足差唔多準備10.1文宣","createTime":"2019-09-04T16:40:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T05:26:33.000Z","uid":55628,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6da0a99c8aecd5ef3bc8b3cd743679c120d791ee","tid":1541900,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:40:21.000Z","msg":"雖然大家都知嗰日會出黎，但活動內容等都差唔多要諗定<br />\n事源9月2-3因文宣不足而令參與罷工人士唔多，而10.1係我哋嘅黃金機會，所以要大大力文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但同時都要繼續做9月活動嘅宣傳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/buJJ0fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbuJJ0fb.png&h=d9bcfbff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/01GC4GS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F01GC4GS.png&h=520955e0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RtUk2tx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRtUk2tx.png&h=fddad37d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋真係有好多人唔上連登，所以連儂牆、隧道、天橋等都要多啲活動資訊，等唔多上網嘅同路人了解活動詳情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勿忘初衷<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"6b30ef79aaa65f813841901a5c412ae0dc1fa985","tid":1541900,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:40:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69cea629bd94d76a227d13f08aa957e8ffdacf38","tid":1541900,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:41:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五</span></span>"},{"pid":"18c4fa8b8500b480c1e6965ee066a1eafc0e213b","tid":1541900,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:42:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大</span></span>"},{"pid":"af3855fcdd1f317ada01b21f412e25a2b48a41be","tid":1541900,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:43:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">訴</span></span>"},{"pid":"ae06f79e173f93a799d24ce8113ac1f34ae5c48e","tid":1541900,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:44:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求</span></span>"},{"pid":"f0d2704b1c61f6066421159544d738a4dd2820e6","tid":1541900,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:45:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">缺</span></span>"},{"pid":"0122da51f970c6db01db8e1545fe14bbb0ad47fd","tid":1541900,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:46:15.000Z","msg":"撤回唔係為咗俾香港人降溫；<br />\n撤回係要分化外國政客、媒體，<br />\n令佢地失去插手香港局面既意慾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人<br />\n